




<h1>George W. Bush<i> (111552331)</i></h1><h3><i> 2005-02-02 - Speeches</i></h3>  To make our <a href='t8.html'><span title='8'><t8>economy</t8></span></a> stronger and more dynamic, we must prepare a <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>rising</t9></span></a> <a href='t3.html'><span title='3'><t3>generation</t3></span></a> to fill the <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>jobs</t9></span></a> of the 21st <a href='t6.html'><span title='6'><t6>century</t6></span></a>. Under the <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>No</t9></span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>Child</t9></span></a> Left Behind <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>Act</t9></span></a>, <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>standards</t9></span></a> are higher, <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>test</t9></span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>scores</t9></span></a> are on the <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>rise</t9></span></a>, and we're closing the <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>achievement</t9></span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>gap</t9></span></a> for <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>minority</t9></span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>students</t9></span></a>. Now we must demand better <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>results</t9></span></a> from our high <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>schools</t9></span></a>, so every high <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>school</t9></span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>diploma</t9></span></a> is a ticket to <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>success</t9></span></a>. We will help an additional 200,000 <a href='t3.html'><span title='3'><t3>workers</t3></span></a> to get <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>training</t9></span></a> for a better <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>career</t9></span></a> by reforming our <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>job</t9></span></a> <a href='t9.html'><span title='9'><t9>training</t9></span></a> <a href='t3.html'><sp